title: When will Fnatic Janna skin be unavailable?
body: I play Janna {{champion:40}} a lot and I am wondering if I should buy it now if it is going do be unavailable very soon.

replies.body:
Hey there!

There's no official date on specifically when Fnatic Skins will be unavailable, but we know other skins made available for MSI are going to be disabled on the May 25th at 16:59 AEST. It's likely the Fnatic skins will be disabled at this time as well.
